parameters: Thank you very much for your help.
So this is the forest Luora mentioned...
It really doesn't feel any different.
Since Luora invited us all this way, I can
assume it won't be the case going forward.
I mean, I do prefer normal things.
For now, let's look for Luora first──
Feels like our first time in Ront.
When we first started our journey
to search for the Lords of Reason, remember?
You asked me to do it, didn't you?
And after so much time passed,
we're now the best of friends.
Well, whatever, let's continue on going.
\C[17]The New Ancient Forest\C[0] has been added to the Event List.
Wanna return to Tantali of Departure?
Tahati said there's a strange place
in Ront, so I came to check it out...
So Luora didn't lead you here?
but Tahati seemed a bit concerned...
Nothing escapes her eyes in all of Parlates.
Well, at least we have the same objective.
Let's help each other out, then.
Will the hunters be fine with you
Well then, let us continue forward, Muracca.
It's just that I'm immediately stuck.
There's some complicated key to this door...
And how about that girl, then?
Some trash keyhole it is, indeed.
I can't believe you got it open so easily...
You truly have many reliable friends, Ino.
I feel blessed to have such great friends.
I'm quite jealous of you both.
Well then, I'll head in a little further.
Spread out in the presence of the unknown.
I want to hump all the males at once!
I feel safe just knowing you're nearby.
\C[17]The New Ancient Forest\C[0]'s details have been updated.
